        "text": "<@UJBAJNFLK> Yes, my heuristic doesn't solve _all_ problems :slightly_smiling_face: For me it shines a light where I care to look for my keys. Attention leads to happiness, cf. <https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Flow_(psychology)|Mihály Csíkszentmihályi> and <https:\/\/www.henrikkarlsson.xyz\/p\/attention|Henrik Karlsson>. You may be able to do things without it, but why would I want to do those things.",
